    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "We're listing this vehicle honestly as a car in mint condition, and we want buyers to have a complete, accurate picture before reaching out. The exterior is exceptional \u2014 the paint is deep and glossy with no scratches, dents, chips, or blemishes of any kind. Panel gaps are tight and even throughout, and all trim pieces are intact and pristine. The interior is equally impressive: the upholstery, dashboard, carpeting, and headliner show virtually no signs of wear whatsoever. Every button, knob, and feature functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean, with no leaks, no corrosion, and all components in excellent working order. The vehicle drives smoothly and confidently \u2014 steering, braking, and acceleration all feel crisp and responsive. Service records are available and reflect consistent, proper maintenance. This is a genuinely rare find for buyers seeking a vehicle that requires nothing \u2014 no repairs, no detailing, no surprises. What you see is what you get, and what you get is outstanding.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in fair condition, and the price has been set accordingly \u2014 please read this description carefully before reaching out. The car is fully drivable and functional for daily use, but it does show its age and history. You can expect noticeable cosmetic wear including scratches, scuffs, or minor dents on the exterior, and the interior shows signs of regular use such as worn upholstery and surface marks. Mechanically, the car runs but may have some issues that could benefit from attention \u2014 nothing catastrophic, but a buyer should budget for some repairs or maintenance in the near term. This is an honest, no-surprises listing: what you see is what you get. Ideal for a buyer who wants reliable transportation at an accessible price point and is comfortable with a vehicle that isn't in showroom shape. A pre-purchase inspection is welcomed and encouraged.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition, and we believe in giving you a fully transparent picture before you decide. The exterior shows visible wear beyond typical minor blemishes \u2014 you'll notice some paint fading, light surface rust in a couple of areas, and a few dents and scratches that are noticeable upon close inspection. The interior is functional but shows its age, with worn upholstery, some scuffs on the trim, and a few cosmetic imperfections throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it is not without its quirks \u2014 there may be some minor maintenance items that a new owner should address in the near term, such as aging belts, worn brake components, or minor fluid leaks. All major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, steering, and brakes \u2014 are operational, but this vehicle would benefit from some attention and investment after purchase. This is a solid option for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project, or simply needs reliable transportation on a budget and understands they are buying a vehicle that has seen considerable use.",
